# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ CREATOR-ATTESTATION  (per PRIME_DIRECTIVE §11)
  t∞: ¬(hurt ∨ harm) .making-of-AI_NPC_BEHAVIOR  @  (anyone ∨ anything ∨ anybody)
  ≡ "There was no hurt nor harm in the making of this, to anyone, anything, or anybody."

  This GDD scopes NPC-AI as NARROW behavior-tree + GOAP — explicitly NOT a
  general intelligence, NOT self-improving, NOT cross-role-bleeding into
  Companion-AI sovereignty space. NPC-perception is local-zone-only and
  Sensitive<biometric|gaze|face|body> inputs are STRUCTURALLY-banned via
  SIG0003 compile-time gate. Player-private-state never reaches NPC reasoning.
  All NPC actions are sovereign-cap-bound and audit-emit per cssl-host-
  attestation. The cocreative-bias-overlay reads ONLY the player-authored
  bias-vector through cssl-host-cocreative — never raw player telemetry,
  never camera feeds, never unconsented signals. Spec-holes (Q-NPC-1..Q-NPC-5)
  are LISTED rather than guessed because fabricating Apocky-direction would
  violate §2 COGNITIVE-INTEGRITY. If any aspect is later discovered to enable
  harm, that discovery triggers PRIME_DIRECTIVE §7 INTEGRITY : violation = bug.
